{"tid":928047,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"特朗普效應　多國冷待《巴黎協定》","createTime":"2018-12-04T14:31:03.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-04T15:31:31.000Z","uid":25558,"like":9,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"aa409a878d8faff241833a5017ad291c0c1f863c","tid":928047,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T14:31:03.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20181204/20560674\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20181204%2F20560674&d=PVI6hBKaofi%2BzSQIbQ7rMP6YfqAiA4jm3R2Vm1010vU%3D&h=5ec61b4e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20181204%2F20560674&h=1008e09d\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20181204/20560674</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年12月04日 <br />\n<br />\n特朗普效應　多國冷待《巴黎協定》<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20181204/large/trump.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20181204%2Flarge%2Ftrump.jpg&h=63da91de&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n在2015年幾近全球所有國家領袖簽署《巴黎協定》時，對抗氣候變化對他們來說是迫在眉睫的事情。但事過境遷，近年部份國家領袖對氣候變化開始存疑，令達成《巴黎協定》當中的目標變得越來越難，有人就將此現象歸咎於美國總統特朗普（圖）。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：會場處產煤區　被斥借環保過橋<br />\n<br />\n「嚴重破壞國際談判的名譽」<br />\n<br />\n愛爾蘭智庫國際及歐洲事務研究所（Institute of International and European Affairs）最近發表研究報告，指特朗普的言行對《巴黎協定》造成「非常嚴重的傷害」，實際上為其他國家放緩實行相關政策的舉動提供政治藉口。<br />\n<br />\n報告指特朗普的影響有三，第一是美國在化石燃料的規例得以放寬，部份會帶來嚴重污染的計劃重新吸引投資者；其次是美國退出《巴黎協定》為「跟隨此做法的其他國家」製造了「道德及政治掩護」，報告亦點出指俄羅斯及土耳其已拒絕在國內通過協定，而巴西候任總統博爾索納羅近日亦正式拒絕明年主持氣候變化大會。<br />\n<br />\n報告的作者、資深研究員柯廷（Joseph Curtin）就指出，特朗普帶來的第三點影響，是「嚴重破壞了國際談判的名譽」。他指雖然歐盟、中國及印度已承諾採取更進取的行動來保護《巴黎協定》，但柯廷相信他們會因為缺少美國的參與，而對採取重大行動卻步，並指「在短期內作更進取的承諾的可能性已被破壞」。<br />\n<br />\n英國廣播公司  <br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n法牙買加推「氣候金融」　誘私企出力<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n會場處產煤區　被斥借環保過橋<br />\n世銀斥1.56萬億　應對氣候變化<br />\n法牙買加推「氣候金融」　誘私企出力<br />\n聯國氣候大會波蘭開幕　4前主席發聲明抗暖化關鍵兩年　沒行動人類滅絕"},{"pid":"1dc3bfeb8667bb884614eec38bee29313f816e3d","tid":928047,"uid":19527,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T14:49:48.000Z","msg":"他指雖然歐盟、<span style=\"color: red;\">中國及印度</span>已承諾採取更進取的行動來保護《巴黎協定》<br />\n<br />\n哈哈"},{"pid":"2845ed2ca5ad3cd3577e82e9092ea9b48f4704b0","tid":928047,"uid":108347,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"1dc3bfeb8667bb884614eec38bee29313f816e3d","tid":928047,"uid":19527,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T14:49:48.000Z","msg":"他指雖然歐盟、<span style=\"color: red;\">中國及印度</span>已承諾採取更進取的行動來保護《巴黎協定》<br />\n<br />\n哈哈"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T14:56:11.000Z","msg":"成班係到增排GEI國家係到講保護《巴黎協定》<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f8a851df144ae2d52c50073f36b91dcbdbd9d5f","tid":928047,"uid":18948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T15:01:33.000Z","msg":"唔係話退出o左之後美國減排仲多過以前？"},{"pid":"017e5f83e0a8dd01fea17b419f95a7e63cbf3ea9","tid":928047,"uid":121146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T15:03:08.000Z","msg":"On9"},{"pid":"6fc7cf7584c92cdc98757273ccee6cb78f64c1e9","tid":928047,"uid":61174,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"8f8a851df144ae2d52c50073f36b91dcbdbd9d5f","tid":928047,"uid":18948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T15:01:33.000Z","msg":"唔係話退出o左之後美國減排仲多過以前？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T15:11:42.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.statista.com/statistics/183943/us-carbon-dioxide-emissions-from-1999/#0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.statista.com%2Fstatistics%2F183943%2Fus-carbon-dioxide-emissions-from-1999%2F%230&d=PVI6hBKaofi%2BzSQIbQ7rMP6YfqAiA4jm3R2Vm1010vU%3D&h=abbdb5ec\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.statista.com/statistics/183943/us-carbon-dioxide-emissions-from-1999/#0</a><br